		<div class="span8 offset1">
			<div class="biography fleft">
				<p><strong>Matt Du Pont<br>(CEO, Yale CS '10)</strong><br>Previously:<br><%= link_to "OkCupid Labs", "http://okcupidlabs.com" %> (Product GM, <%= link_to "Kiss.com", "http://www.kiss.com" %>)<br><%= link_to "BCG", "http://www.bcg.com" %> (Associate)</p>
